<div class=panel-separator></div><div class="panel-pane pane-views-panes pane-news-details-panel-pane-10 no-title block">
<div class="view view-news-details view-id-news_details view-display-id-panel_pane_10 author-name view-dom-id-311cfb27eea7a347651ecdf1862bce4b">
<h1> Tussle with KEPZ earns Bangladesh bad name </h1>
<h5> <em>Analysts say at discussion co-organised by MCCI and SANEM</em> </h5>
</div>
</div>
<div class=panel-separator></div><div class="panel-pane pane-block pane-block-7 in-news d-hide tm-show pane-block no-title block">
<script src="//s7.addthis.com/js/300/addthis_widget.js" async></script>
<div class="addthis_toolbox addthis_32x32_style">
